# 10 – REDESIM Email Extractor Rules

- Python **3.9+**; orchestrate via Make targets `make setup|dev|test|draft|status`.
- Gmail OAuth scope restricted to **compose-only**; tokens stored locally (`GMAIL_CREDENTIALS_PATH`, `GMAIL_TOKEN_PATH`).
- Draft automation must filter addresses containing `@sefaz.pb.gov.br`.
- Chrome extension stays on Manifest V3 with minimal permissions (`activeTab`, `storage`, `downloads`, `notifications`).
- Batch executor command:  
  ```bash
  python3 /absolute/path/to/redesim-email-extractor/batch_process_emails.py
  ```
- Recommended env vars: `REDESIM_BASE_URL`, `DOWNLOAD_PATH`.
- Provide pytest targets + coverage hints; validate extension scripts with `node -c`.
- Respect privacy-first posture; no external data syncing.

